OL,3,CUK inflation steady but food and drink
OL,4,Ccosts continue to climb
OL,6,FThe headline annual rate of inflation
OL,7,Fin the UK held steady in August.
OL,9,FPrices are still rising by 3.8% a year
OL,10,F- the same pace as in July - but
OL,11,Fthat's faster than the Bank of England
OL,12,Fis willing to tolerate.
OL,14,FThe Bank's job is to keep inflation
OL,15,Flow and stable at 2%.
OL,17,FOne year ago, inflation was below that
OL,18,Ftarget.
