OL,3,CUK inflation steady but food and drink
OL,4,Ccosts continue to climb
OL,6,FThe "cost of living" has been steadily
OL,7,Fdriven higher by repeated increases in
OL,8,Fthe prices of fuel, food, and energy,
OL,9,Fas well as some one-off jumps in water
OL,10,Fbills and vehicle excise duties.
OL,12,F"I know families are finding it tough
OL,13,Fand that for many the economy feels
OL,14,Fstuck. That's why I'm determined to
OL,15,Fbring costs down and support people
OL,16,Fwho are facing higher bills," the
OL,17,FChancellor said in a statement this
OL,18,Fmorning.
