OL,3,CUK inflation steady but food and drink
OL,4,Ccosts continue to climb
OL,6,FLast month, the Bank of England said a
OL,7,Fnew packaging scheme designed to
OL,8,Freduce waste, introduced by the last
OL,9,Fgovernment but adopted by this one,
OL,10,Fwill push food prices up further.
OL,12,FIt expects food inflation to peak at
OL,13,F5.5% at Christmas before falling
OL,14,Fgradually in 2026. Higher food prices
OL,15,Fget noticed because they hurt, and
OL,16,Fhurt those on lower incomes in
OL,17,Fparticular.
