OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThere are many ways to measure what is
OL,12,Fhappening to prices.
OL,14,F"Core" inflation, which strips out
OL,15,Ffood and energy prices, eased to 3.6%.
OL,17,FInflation in the services sector of
OL,18,Fthe economy, which tends to better
OL,19,Freflect wage growth, also dipped to
OL,20,F4.7%.
